  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t中国共匪的黑爷爷黑奶奶现在数量大增繁殖飞快，完全没有老龄化现象，计划生育天方夜谭！<b>且黑种儿爱国无上限没下限</b>，<b>奔放豪迈，随时随地，伸展舒适，</b><b>床头被窝边操边攻读</b>习二儿《<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\">通商宽衣</a></b>》著作不断：全部斯瓦希里语版本！以后《<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41281\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41281\"><b>习近平著作</b></a>》斯瓦希里语版印刷量大超汉语版本印量，中式黄黑五毛杂种从出生伊始便高声朗诵《<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\">通商宽衣</a></b>》内容，倒背如流，经常摘引习大马棒诸如“遗屎弃纸”，“老人瞻仰” 等惊世名句招摇过市，摇头晃脑，朗声喧嚣，口沫飞溅，旁若无人，倨傲猖狂，身旁路边黄种奴才唯唯诺诺低声下气不敢侧目，唯恐惊扰了共匪主子的黑非洲爷爷享受通商宽衣美好时光，糟蹋故国山河。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS82amtHZW42LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/6jkGen6.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6jkGen6.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6jkGen6.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9ySHkyanRrLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/rHy2jtk.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rHy2jtk.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rHy2jtk.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9XcGx1b1poLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpluoZh.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpluoZh.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpluoZh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9EMFVWdXRkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0UVutd.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0UVutd.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0UVutd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/